dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.corecommunication

Interface IDynamicPart

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IMultiplexedPart

    public interface IDynamicPart
extends IEntity, IMultiplexedPart
    IDynamicPart: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Dynamic part of a multiplexed I-Pdu. Reserved space which is used to transport varying SignalIPdus at the same position, controlled by the corresponding selectorFieldCode.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!

        long getSelectorFieldCode()
        Query the value of the attribute SelectorFieldCode.

        The selector field is part of a multiplexed IPdu. It consists of contiguous bits. The value of the selector field selects the layout of the multiplexed part of the IPdu.

        The value or null
